The `sbb-seat-reservation-navigation` allows the user to navigate between the individual transport wagons. Useful information about the individual wagons should also be presented here

```html
<sbb-seat-reservation-navigation seatReservation="seatReservationObj<SeatReservation>">
</sbb-seat-reservation-navigation>
```
